                              </figcaption>
                      </figure>
        </li>
              <li data-thumb="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/FP2_Launch_Screenshots_Idea_Tree-150x150.jpg" data-src="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/FP2_Launch_Screenshots_Idea_Tree.jpg" data-responsive="https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/FP2_Launch_Screenshots_Idea_Tree-980x551.jpg 1080, https://cdn.arstechnica.net/wp-content/uploads/2024/09/FP2_Launch_Screenshots_Idea_Tree-1440x810.jpg 2560" data-sub-html="#caption-2051263">
